1
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,340
[Bride's Revenge]

2
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:31,780
[Episode 17]

3
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:34,780
[The Return of an Old Acquaintance]

4
00:00:35,260 --> 00:00:39,700
[Half a year later]

5
00:00:56,390 --> 00:00:57,000
(Anhe,)

6
00:00:57,790 --> 00:00:59,470
(I was going to leave)

7
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:00,920
(after avenging you.)

8
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:02,640
(But that monster, Mu Ancheng,)

9
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:05,480
(killed Mother.)

10
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:09,870
(And the family of the first son of Ye
is eyeing Mu Family's wealth.)

11
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,230
(I must protect this family for you.)

12
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:16,430
(Mu Ancheng has been arrested,)

13
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,400
(but it has been so long,)

14
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:20,640
(and he is yet to be convicted.)

15
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:23,200
(That animal would do anything)

16
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,200
(to keep himself safe.)

17
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,950
(I heard that he has been forming connections)

18
00:01:28,790 --> 00:01:31,120
(in hopes that he would be freed one day.)

19
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:35,790
I'll never let him get away with it.

20
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,560
First Young Madam!

21
00:01:39,350 --> 00:01:40,640
First Young Madam! Bad news!

22
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,680
A message came from the Ye Family.

23
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,070
Your father's illness acted up and he fainted!

24
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,760
What?

25
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:46,870
I'll go back at once.

26
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,150
That idiot Mu Ancheng!

27
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:55,070
I thought I would get to live
a life of wealth and comfort with him!

28
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:57,310
But he has been detained for so long,
and he still hasn't gotten himself out yet.

29
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,070
He'll probably never get out of there.

30
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,350
I need to leave

31
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,640
before I get dragged down with him.

32
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:05,510
First Young Madam returned home in a hurry.

33
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:06,590
Really?

34
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,360
With Ye Qinglan away,

35
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,840
this is my chance to leave.

36
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,190
Prepare the carriage.

37
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:12,870
We'll leave now.

38
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:35,820
[Mu's Residence]

39
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:49,750
First…

40
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:50,800
First Young Master…

41
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,150
What about him?

42
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,400
First Young Master has returned!

43
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,360
What?

44
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,800
How is that possible?

45
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:06,030
(You think you can keep me in jail forever)

46
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,430
(with that little bit of evidence?)

47
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,710
(How naive.)

48
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:16,630
(From now on, the Mu Family is mine.)

49
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:23,750
Ancheng?

50
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,590
Why are you back?

51
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,030
Naturally, I was found innocent and released

52
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,030
due to insufficient evidence.

53
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,120
First Young Master!

54
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,430
You're finally home!

55
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,710
I felt like my world was falling apart

56
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,310
when you were gone.

57
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:37,710
There, there.

58
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,190
I'm back now.

59
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:42,870
Are you really out of trouble now?

60
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,360
I'm already home.

61
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,680
What else could happen to me?

62
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:52,080
Where's Qinglan?

63
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,130
She went back to her natal family.

64
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,840
At a time like this?

65
00:03:58,310 --> 00:04:00,560
Yes. Ever since you were arrested

66
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,000
and your mother passed away,

67
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:03,710
things have been a mess in the residence.

68
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,470
First Young Madam went back home

69
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,710
to avoid everything.

70
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,960
She doesn't care at all.

71
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,310
Send someone to bring her back!

72
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:12,470
Yes.

73
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,190
What are you guys standing around for?

74
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,310
Don't you see that First Young Master is home?

75
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,190
Hurry up and clean all this mess!

76
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:21,800
Yes.

77
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,600
What's all this?

78
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,240
You've been detained

79
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,310
for so long.

80
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,160
So I thought

81
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,070
I should pawn these valuables

82
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:33,190
to get some money

83
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:35,120
and see if I could bail you out

84
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,480
at the police station.

85
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:43,360
True love endures in times of crisis.

86
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:46,430
As long as I can save you, this is nothing.

87
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:48,430
How come you are released?

88
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,190
What?

89
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:55,750
Are you not happy that I've been released?

90
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,190
That's not it.

91
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:00,190
Of course I am happy.

92
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,830
I'm just surprised.

93
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,630
You don't seem happy at all

94
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,750
to me.

95
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,270
What happened?

96
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:12,920
I couldn't see you
even when I tried to pull some strings.

97
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:15,360
Why did the police let you out so easily?

98
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,000
I was wrongly accused in the first place.

99
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,680
Once they learned the truth,

100
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,750
of course, they had to release me.

101
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:23,800
That's great.

102
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,750
I'm glad you were able to clear your name.

103
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:34,270
Master, you've lost weight.

104
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,040
You're considerate indeed.

105
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:39,680
(To think he actually managed to bribe the police)

106
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:41,600
(and got out of there in one piece.)

107
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,870
(Mu Ancheng,)

108
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,830
(if the police can't do anything to you,)

109
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,600
(I'll go to Mr. Jin.)

110
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,070
(Someone in this city)

111
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:52,870
(must be able to teach you a lesson.)

112
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,310
Aren't you the wife of Mr. Mu?

113
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,920
What brings you here?

114
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,920
Something that will make you rich.

115
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,430
Tell me more.

116
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,120
I'll give you a reason

117
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:18,390
to extort money from Mu Ancheng.

118
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:26,630
Are you a couple or enemies?

119
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:31,510
I'm sure you've heard of the incident

120
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,430
regarding the Second Young Master
of the Mu Family

121
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:34,950
being kidnapped and killed?

122
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:36,480
I've heard about it.

123
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,120
I heard the First Young Master
was wrongly arrested.

124
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,510
He was later proven to be innocent

125
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,560
and released.

126
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,680
He is the culprit.

127
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,510
And it's substantiated by evidence.

128
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,510
He used underhand tactics

129
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,680
to get out of prison.

130
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,950
Otherwise, how could you not have been made aware

131
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:54,800
of such a serious matter happening

132
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,920
under your nose?

133
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:02,600
I did try to investigate which gang

134
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,040
was behind this case,

135
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:06,630
but I found nothing.

136
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,750
So I suspected

137
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:11,190
it was the work of someone in the Mu Family.

138
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,270
Mu Ancheng abducted Second Young Master

139
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,480
and extorted a large sum of money

140
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:17,870
from the Mu and Ye Families.

141
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,830
After that, he killed him in cold blood.

142
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,510
What a heartless guy.

143
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,120
Killing his own brother.

144
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,240
I know you hold justice and righteousness

145
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:34,600
in high regard, Mr. Jin.

146
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,480
So I want to give you a chance

147
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,680
to rob the rich and help the poor.

148
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:03,720
Second Master, this matter…

149
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:16,380
♪The tangle of love and hate between us♪

150
00:08:16,620 --> 00:08:19,980
♪Caused me to regret it♪

151
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:26,180
♪I'm afraid we can't change our fate in this life♪

152
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:30,340
♪I do not fear. I do not hide♪

153
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:33,820
♪I can no longer bear the pain♪

154
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:41,020
♪It grows as time passes♪

155
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:43,260
♪Time will not tell you♪

156
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,300
♪That I have been missing you♪

157
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:48,060
♪You are all I think about♪

158
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,020
♪No matter♪

159
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,460
♪How harshly♪

160
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:55,140
♪Life treats me♪

161
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:57,180
♪I can only let go of my hate♪

162
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:58,900
♪Not my love♪

163
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:02,780
♪We promised each other life-long love♪

164
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:09,260
♪Hopefully, we will keep that promise♪
